Registry, Started, 	ProviderName=Registry
	NewProviderState=Started

	SequenceNumber=1

	HostName=ConsoleHost
	HostVersion=5.1.19041.5007
	HostId=336cdb4b-bfa9-42a4-a67b-ead1ab70e201
	HostApplication=powershell.exe & {New-PSDrive -PSProvider registry -Root HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT -Name HKCR
Get-ChildItem -Path HKCR:\CLSID -Name | Select -Skip 1 > $env:temp\clsids.txt
ForEach($CLSID in Get-Content "$env:temp\clsids.txt")
{try{write-output "$($Position)-$($CLSID)"
write-output "------------"| out-file $env:temp\data.002Test1.txt -append
write-output $($CLSID)| out-file $env:temp\data.002Test1.txt -append
$handle=[activator]::CreateInstance([type]::GetTypeFromCLSID($CLSID))
$handle | get-member -erroraction silentlycontinue | out-file $env:temp\data.002Test1.txt -append
$position += 1} catch{}}}

	PipelineId=
